@.\"	$OpenBSD: portmap.8,v 1.8 2010/12/16 20:22:07 jmc Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 1987 Sun Microsystems
.\" Copyright (c) 1990, 1991 The Regents of the University of California.
.\" All rights reserved.
